content:
Assign custom permission sets to one or more users—either one at a time, or in bulk—to give them access to CRM Analytics functionality.

To assign a permission set to users:

* In the Setup menu, click Users | Permission Sets and then click New.
* Click the permission set you want to assign to users. Select either the Manage CRM Analytics or View CRM Analytics permission sets.
* Click Manage Assignments and click Add Assignments.
* Select the users who need access to CRM Analytics, and click Done.

When you assign the permission set to users, Salesforce auto-assigns the CRM Analytics Cloud - CRM Analytics Platform permission set license to those users.
title: Assigning Permissions in Salesforce CRM Analytics
